{"tid":1925492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本豪捐47億台幣給WHO 譚德塞稱讚：安倍防疫踏出關鍵一步","createTime":"2020-03-14T12:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T14:25:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"46e3bdb13add3db26eed3eef6eb947a0aa42eec0","tid":1925492,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情爆發以來，世界衛生組織（ WHO ）的功能與表現備受質疑，甚至有網友向美國白宮請願，請求美國政府提名我國衛福部長陳時中取代 WHO 現任秘書長譚德塞（ Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ）。而譚德塞最近又有爭議發言，大讚安倍防疫表現，被懷疑是因為收了日本 1.55 億美元、約新台幣 47 億元的捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《阿拉伯新聞》報導，譚德塞昨日在日內瓦舉行的記者會上，不僅直言歐洲「已經成為疫情大流行的中心」，他還特別點名讚揚了日本首相安倍晉三，認為安倍親自帶領日本政府以及專家團隊投入防疫，在減緩病毒傳染上踏出了關鍵的一步。<br />\n<br />\n不僅日本，譚德塞也認為中國大陸、韓國、新加坡等國的經驗表明，積極的病毒篩檢以及有效隔離，可以遏止病毒傳播並拯救生命。譚德塞最後感謝日本捐助了 1.55 億美元給 WHO ，強調這筆捐款將用來添購防疫設備。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸的疫情按照對岸官方數字來看已經趨緩，而新加坡和韓國的防疫經驗，確實也是被不少專家提及。但是日本的防疫表現，一直以來罕有被誇獎，甚至不時會被拿出來當「反面教材」。譚德塞點名稱讚安倍，又感謝日本捐款，不免讓外界把這兩件事聯想在一起。（編輯：倪浩軒）"},{"pid":"dde9e2a8f30fde7b4b62e533a05550e31309875e","tid":1925492,"uid":52090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口交費用"},{"pid":"182fc83d7ecd455bfd274ad3421f20a6192b39ea","tid":1925492,"uid":3457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:02:51.000Z","msg":"比錢就踏出一步 <br />\n唔比錢就透明度唔夠"},{"pid":"c1790cc8859547ea1cb6d722d5bfdf631564038b","tid":1925492,"uid":83713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"為左奧運姐，都唔使折墮到咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a882b2c4acfc63d7f8ce4e754bc39117301d8f97","tid":1925492,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"支那都係兩千萬美金，日本捐1.55億？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b733a669a82adda0b12ba4baa696bb4d7a83c5d3","tid":1925492,"uid":35266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3130d93c407f1728a200cad39619906be6cfdb2b","tid":1925492,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"入錢入錢入錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5569771360e9c236e56dc02b3b6a0c6619a35c","tid":1925492,"uid":5813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線日本，好學唔學學支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇死你個奧運都搞唔成架啦"},{"pid":"dcca620b87654140159386fc386db5c6ca81bd02","tid":1925492,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"香港人又笑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港政府唔知捐左幾多錢比香港人日日喊打喊殺既中共，但香港人次次都硬食，依家搵到位笑日本仔，仲唔威返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cd756a36d11be1be9be5a4134e9ce1d683628c","tid":1925492,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"唔講政治野 其實捐世衛有咩用 談道德日日出黎9up有無實際貢獻"},{"pid":"3cc1567d8e8ac717889b10648258f0b730f5bb21","tid":1925492,"uid":81968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"世衛：捐錢可以防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cfeef043a8a29f43e90036e9afb6571c325703","tid":1925492,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本人"},{"pid":"d2671fd9d9a89